# loki-shell drop patterns
# One extended regex (ERE) per line. Commands matching any pattern will NOT be sent to Loki.
# Lines starting with # are ignored by grep.
#
# Examples:
#
# Drop commands containing a password-like argument
# --password[= ].+
#
# Drop ssh/scp commands with inline passwords
# sshpass .+
#
# Drop export of sensitive environment variables
# export .*(PASSWORD|SECRET|TOKEN|KEY)=.+
#
# Drop commands matching partial password (first and last few chars with wildcard)
# abc.+xyz
